reviewText: Fascinating history of DIY music. He does a great job of putting the history of Cigar Box Guitars, which are all DIY, into the broader history of all homemade contraptions that you can use to make music.
Awesome story on Cigar Box guitars. It make me want to make one. Heck, now my wife wants to make one after watching this.
It was okay, just wish there was more playing then there was.
The movie truly captured the essence of the modern cigar box guitar community, accompanied by a great historic narrative.
Awesome movie,found it to be informative and entertaining.
Excellent music, awesome playing cigar box guitars by great artists!
Not great quality but very interesting
Awesome story. Jon Miller has outdone himself in this incredible video!
